{"tid":2304280,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【今晚有牌打】林文龍被達哥問題考起　唔記得邊年同郭可盈結婚？","createTime":"2020-11-28T15:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T15:37:34.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0be4b5384175bbeba361b09d338c2d6ee7318c07","tid":2304280,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"曾擔任亞視擔任副總裁、現已轉職為亞洲心動娛樂（AMM）香港區副總裁的林文龍，早前與電玩達人林慧韡（達哥）拍攝AMM新麻將遊戲節目《今晚有牌打》，而節目的前傳亦於昨日（27/11）正式出爐。片中，達哥以「社交平台媒體形象指導員」身份教林文龍玩Instagram，不但逼林文龍大擺日本動漫《JoJo奇妙冒險》經典甫士，又安排林文龍接受打機特訓。在邊打機邊快問快答環節中，達哥便問林文龍哪年與老婆郭可盈結婚，豈料林文龍一時間答不出，更抱頭尷尬微笑：「二零零&hellip;&hellip;死喇，突然之間好亂呀！」嚇到達哥以為自己問了一個不應該問的問題，而他幾經辛苦才想起兩人是2004年結婚，非常搞笑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uon5Cl0PoV4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUon5Cl0PoV4&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoRzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=3a41268c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uon5Cl0PoV4</a>"},{"pid":"ade18f2b7061fd370340ee346f9d0bdd2fe93b3c","tid":2304280,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T15:35:30.000Z","msg":"&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790481bed0b26ad95d95d72efa69b643826f936f","tid":2304280,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T15:37:34.000Z","msg":"一直關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}